{"tid":470084,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普因病入院缺操","createTime":"2017-11-16T03:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T03:25:11.000Z","uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0875d6576fa5eeea0ad4014801e9876c089e813c","tid":470084,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:07:31.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=HEhLnMtwE8kNTIt9u6ef2AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=83217c8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦領隊高普周三因病入院，暫時未有住院的需要，不過未知道能否在周六的英超領軍。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦在聲明中表示：「高普（Jurgen Klopp）感到身體不適，為了安全起見在周三到醫院接受檢查，因此缺席了操練。」幸好，高普未有要住院的需要，在較後時間將會回家休息，不過在未來數天要再作詳細檢查。<br />\n<br />\n紅軍又指，希望外界尊重這名50歲德國藉主帥、其家人、同院病人的私隱。在剛過去的國際賽期，高普抽空到了南非度假，但未知跟今次生病有沒有關係。<br />\n<br />\n周六英超，利物浦將在主場迎戰修咸頓，要是高普未能領軍，將會由其助手卡華韋斯及保華錫帶領球隊。高普在2016年2月，曾因為盲腸炎而缺席了利物浦主場鬥新特蘭的英超，當時紅軍只能跟對方踢成2:2。"},{"pid":"a5d3a243628b579f5fb2d214e6c5adc510d7b314","tid":470084,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:09:21.000Z","msg":"有激情不必怕"},{"pid":"001364d8c13c4dae35fb0ffa733b3df150db8e00","tid":470084,"uid":12680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:10:01.000Z","msg":"條腸比痢班垃圾激到彈起"},{"pid":"b234e0aee6e7e6f24a5a058b1f6fe38143f5cd42","tid":470084,"uid":33601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:18:26.000Z","msg":"見到痢踢成咁 我都入院啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n笑到入院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab15f068120fc481552c852d760291e53f1a584","tid":470084,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:18:33.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"d077edea685f6622fa7a8b18bbe67e8142e00dac","tid":470084,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:22:29.000Z","msg":"唱返首you'll never walk alone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f567c47101a7ce65575ba934dbe8a95102b8be","tid":470084,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:25:11.000Z","msg":"佢會唔會好似沙高咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/001737_c9ee7f13e67938c2a8518cc16f093651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F001737_c9ee7f13e67938c2a8518cc16f093651.jpg&h=b3c4cdb4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}